channel.title: DJ Vreg ft. Akon ft. Chris Brown ft. Jason Derulo - Whatcha Say
channel.description:
Alright after I had many bad reactions at my previous remixes I made another one wich I hope you guys think is better, remember a remix doesn't have to be nessecary better than the original song so don't start telling me the original is better, DON'T say it's shit, if you can't resist telling me it's shit also tell me WHY it's shit, this is my 4th remix ever.
DJ Vreg ft. Akon ft. Chris Brown ft. Jason Derulo - Whatcha Say:
